# Naming Conventions

**Slug:** lowercase `{leadauthor}-{year}-{short-title}` derived from PDF filename, e.g. `he-2025-dynfed` from `He et al. - 2025 - DynFed...pdf`.

**Paths:**
- PDF: `papers/<original-filename>.pdf`
- Markdown: `markdown/{slug}/paper.md`, `meta.yaml`
- Summary: `summaries/drafts/{slug}.md` then `summaries/{slug}.md`

Align bibkeys in `bib/references.bib` with slugs where possible.
